{"title":"Polar Verity Sense optical heart rate monitor sensor provides alternative to chest straps","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/10/polar-verity-sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-sensor-provides-alternative-to-chest-straps/","date":1612947601000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Polar’s new optical Verity Sense heart rate sensor could be a better option for athletes who struggle with fit or consistent data from conventional heart rate monitor chest straps. Using the same LED-based measurement tech found in Polar’s smart watches now paired to almost any device, Verity Sense can be strapped to your arm or temple to track your efforts, even storing workout data on its own to be synced later.</p><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xkjSBrV0wS4?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\"></iframe></span></p><p>Developed as a better heart rate tracking solution for sports where a chest strap doesn’t always offer the best fit or performance (<em>think: swimming or weight training</em>), the new optical Polar Verity Sense upgrades on the capabilities of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/06/18/polar-beat-heart-rate-trackers-get-free-smart-phone-powered-smart-coaching/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">previous generation OH1</a> optical sensor.</p><figure id=\"attachment_251238\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-251238\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training.jpg\" alt=\"Polar Verity Sense optical heart rate monitor strap alternative update, Boxing cross-training\" width=\"1200\" height=\"720\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-700x420.jpg 700w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_boxing-cross-training-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-251238\">c. Polar</figcaption></figure><p>And it can probably be a great option for many cyclists too. Specifically, one of our own team has fought with conventional electronic pulse-based heart rate straps for years. We suspect that she often doesn’t sweat enough while riding to maintain sufficient conduction between the strap &amp; her skin, often resulting in data dropout especially in cooler weather or on longer, lower-intensity endurance rides.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><h3>Optical heart rate tracking – Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband.jpg\" alt=\"Polar Verity Sense optical heart rate monitor strap alternative update, with armband\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-700x420.jpg 700w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-with-armband-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a></p><p>Verity Sense uses the same 6 LED optical heart tracking as the previous OH1, which placed securely against the skin promises accurate effort tracking. Polar sells it with the armband to secure to the upper arm or clip to secure under a swim goggle strap. But you can also just place it against the skin anywhere that tight-fitting clothing will keep it firmly in place.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views.jpg\" alt=\"Polar Verity Sense optical heart rate monitor strap alternative update, sensor angled detail\" width=\"2000\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-d