ive-update_sensor-detail-views-297x134.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views-800x360.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views-120x54.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views-768x346.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views-1536x691.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views-696x313.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views-1068x481.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views-1920x864.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_sensor-detail-views-933x420.jpg 933w\"></a></p><p>Now with the addition of 4x as much internal memory storage, you can store up to 600 hours of heart rate data, before you even need to sync it back to your phone. One button activation starts it recording even though your clothing (and no licking the sensors required!) In the pool, it will apparently also track distance &amp; pace automatically, in addition to heart rate.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_PolarFlow-ecosystem.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_PolarFlow-ecosystem.jpg\" alt=\"Polar Verity Sense optical heart rate monitor strap alternative update, PolarFlow\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_PolarFlow-ecosystem.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_PolarFlow-ecosystem.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_PolarFlow-ecosystem-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_PolarFlow-ecosystem-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_PolarFlow-ecosystem-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-rate-monitor-strap-alternative-update_PolarFlow-ecosystem-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Polar-Verity-Sense-optical-heart-ra